description: Number of nonisomorphic cyclic subgroups of general linear group GL(n,2).
references: V. Jovovic, The cycle index polynomials of some classical groups, Belgrade, 1995, unpublished.
example: a(5)=13 because the orders of the elements of GL(5,2) are {1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,12,14,15,21,31}.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Mar 22 2000
